  lines:
  - speakerName: Iroha
    avatar: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 681f82db4902e9a4fa3fe39f7f30c840, type: 3}
    content: (Nervously) I... I think this batch came out right! Please, try it,
      Kaguya
  - speakerName: Kaguya
    avatar: {fileID: 21300000, guid: ca85ad29208a0e346b547ca4d8a6e937, type: 3}
    content: (Her eyes sparkle as she takes a bite.) Mmm! Iroha!
  - speakerName: Kaguya
    avatar: {fileID: 21300000, guid: ca85ad29208a0e346b547ca4d8a6e937, type: 3}
    content: They're absolutely perfect! Fluffy, sweet, and melt-in-your-mouth delicious!
  - speakerName: Iroha
    avatar: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 681f82db4902e9a4fa3fe39f7f30c840, type: 3}
    content: (Beams with pride and relief) Really?! Oh, I'm so happy!
  - speakerName: Kaguya
    avatar: {fileID: 21300000, guid: ca85ad29208a0e346b547ca4d8a6e937, type: 3}
    content: See? I knew you could do it. You're the best, Iroha!
